    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_001749_0001" n="0001"/><!-- Change both @facs and @n -->
<lb/><fw n="55"><add place="margintop" rend="gray right" hand="#U">55</add></fw>
<lb/><opener><dateline rend="right"><placeName>Shupanga</placeName> <date when="1862-03-15">15<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> March
<lb/> 1862</date></dateline>
<lb/>    
<lb/><salute>My Dear M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Rowley</salute></opener>
<lb/><p>
<lb/>this is a terrible
<lb/>blow to the mission &amp;
<lb/>makes me very much depressed in view
<lb/>of the effect it will
<lb/>have on all our
<lb/>efforts - <!-- unclear word --> we
<lb/>must not swerve
<lb/>from the work we
<lb/>have undertaken
<lb/>come what will and I trust you will all
<lb/>feel the importance 
<lb/><cb rend="vertical"/><p>
In January &amp; She is much too deep along
<lb/>Excuse thus hasty note we are starting
</p>

	<pb facs="liv_001749_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/>of sticking more closely
<lb/>together and supporting
<lb/>each other than ever - 
<lb/>Remember <unclear cert="medium">pray</unclear> that
<lb/>the eyes of the most
<lb/>influential people in
<lb/><placeName><settlement type="country">England</settlement></placeName> are upon you 
<lb/>and should anything
<lb/>present you doing
<lb/>your duty <unclear cert="medium">merrifully</unclear>
<lb/>you will be set down
<lb/>as a parcel of <unclear cert="low">writing</unclear>
<lb/>hypocrites that ought 
<lb/>never to have been <w>en<supplied></supplied>
<lb break="no"/>trusted</w> with anything
<lb/>Let every little difference
<lb/>dwindle into insignificance
<lb/>before the great work <!-- unclear if this is an &amp;, a squiggle, or in someone else's hand -JZ-->
<lb/><cb rend="vertical"/><p>for the sea hoping this may find you</p>

	<pb facs="liv_001749_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/><fw n="56"><add place="margintop" rend="gray right" hand="#U">56</add></fw>
<lb/>in which you are engaged
<lb/><unclear cert="low">excuse</unclear> my saing so 
<lb/>much in the <unclear cert="low">hortarery</unclear>
<lb/>style - 
</p>
<p><lb/>We could not carry up 
<lb/>35 tons of the new steamer
<lb/>took 3 weeks to come
<lb/>up to <placeName><settlement type="village">Shupanga</settlement></placeName> - <w>un<supplied></supplied> 
<lb break="no"/>headed</w> 5 tons there - tried
<lb/>again and were forced 
<lb/>to unload all - put her
<lb/>together and tow her up
<lb/>in May next - you
<lb/>will see how entirely
<lb/>it is out of our power
<lb/>to serve you with this
<lb/>steamer as I would - 
<lb/>We are entirely out of
<lb/>provisions - and have 
<lb/>no prospect of getting
<cb rend="vertical"/><p>in health &amp; good spirits <closer><salute>I am the</salute>
<lb/><signed><persName>David Livingstone</persName></signed></closer>

	<pb facs="liv_001749_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/>any except by going to
<lb/><placeName>Johanna</placeName><!-- short for Johannesburg? should I denote this as a city? -JZ --> - and should
<lb/>we be too late for the
<lb/>ascent of the <app><rdg cert="medium">Shine</rdg><rdg>Shire</rdg></app> will
<lb/>lose a season - then
<lb/>he <term type="occupation">bishop</term> came down
<lb/>in Nov<hi rend="sup underline"><unclear cert="medium">&amp;</unclear></hi> he wished to go
<lb/>down to the <settlement type="river">Ruo</settlement> &amp; explore
<lb/>upwards but I objected
<lb/>very strongly as the <seg type="weather">rain</seg>
<lb/>fell every afternoon and
<lb/>would knock him up -
<lb/>Well we went down one day
<lb/>and then were detained over
<lb/><!-- should I mark as a "measure"? -->6 weeks with a large marsh
<lb/>on each side of us &amp; lost
<lb/>our first man in the
<lb/>expedition - we stood two
<lb/>days <measure>1 mile above</measure> <settlement type="river">Ruo</settlement> but 
<lb/>on 1<hi rend="sup underline">st</hi> January <unclear cert="low">and</unclear> <term type="occupation">bishop</term>
<lb/>could be heard of - We did
<lb/>not reach the sea till late
</p>
